  <description>
    <p>
      A GUI Plugin and Template Manager for FrayTools, that helps you manage your plugins and templates. 
    </p>
    <p> Currently supports: </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Viewing Changelogs</li>
      <li>Downloading, Installing, and Uninstalling Plugins and Templates</li>
      <li>Convenient Version Swapping</li>
      <li>Builtin Plugin detection for existing plugins and templates</li>
      <li>Supports all the official plugins and templates out of the box</li>
      <li>Caches Plugin and Template downloads for fast reinstallations</li>
      <li>Supports adding custom plugin sources outside the official ones</li>
      <li>Editing And Template Sources</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

